      <recruitment_details>Enrolled patients with a BG 140-400 mg/dL with DM for more than 3 months,aged 18-80 yo, treated with diet alone, any combination of oral antidiabetic agents, or lowdose insulin in 2008-2009. Study was conducted at Grady Memorial Hospital,Emory University Hospitaland the Veterans Administration Medical Center.</recruitment_details>
